# ADMIN FEATURES

Customers:

* NO login required

Admin:

* login visible ONLY when admin chooses to manage/edit

Temporary credentials:

* username: admin
* password: test

Admin capabilities:

* add paintings
* edit paintings
* remove paintings
* persist changes to SQLite

---

# ADMIN WINDOW REQUIREMENTS

Clicking:

`Manage Artwork`

must:

* open a FULL-SCREEN admin management window
* overlay entire application
* include circular close button with “X”
* support keyboard escape close
* include:

  * Add Artwork
  * Edit Artwork
  * Remove Artwork
  * Save Artwork
* Editing mode must allow:

  * image changes
  * title changes
  * description changes
  * price changes
  * availability changes
  * PayPal data changes
  * dimensions
  * medium
  * category
* Remove must include confirmation flow
* Prevent accidental deletion

---

# API + STORAGE REQUIREMENTS

Required API endpoints:

* paintings
* offers
* requests

PayPal seller email MUST be configurable in:

`mtk-gallery.config.js`

SQLite requirements:

* real tables required
* no empty placeholder DB
* persist:

  * paintings
  * offers
  * requests
  * admin edits

