# FAILURE PREVENTION RULES

DO NOT:

* use placeholder code
* omit required files
* generate partial implementations
* break existing requirements
* replace Vanilla JS with frameworks
* compile SCSS globally
* load SCSS directly in browser
* expose passwords in UI
* create empty SQLite DB structure without tables
* create fake API routes
* create recursive rendering
* create DOM replacement loops
* create blank screen behavior
* create blinking render loops

Ensure ALL generated files are runnable together.

